    <br>(d) Find the equation of AB. <span class="marks-badge">3</span></div>
    <button class="memo-toggle" onclick="toggleMemo(this)">📋 Show Memo</button>
    <div class="memo-content">
      <strong>(a)</strong> AB = √[(4−(−2))² + (2−4)²] = √[36+4] = √40 = 2√10 ✓ (2)<br><br>
      <strong>(b)</strong> m_BC = (−4−2)/(2−4) = −6/−2 = 3 ✓ (2)<br><br>
      <strong>(c)</strong> m_AB = (2−4)/(4−(−2)) = −2/6 = −1/3<br>
