    <br>(b) cos2θ = −½ [Hint: let 2θ = x] <span class="marks-badge">4</span>
    <br>(c) tanθ + √3 = 0 <span class="marks-badge">4</span></div>
    <button class="memo-toggle" onclick="toggleMemo(this)">📋 Show Memo</button>
    <div class="memo-content">
      <strong>(a)</strong> sinθ = ½ → ref = 30°<br>
      θ = 30° + 360°n  OR  θ = 150° + 360°n,  n∈ℤ ✓ (4)<br><br>
      <strong>(b)</strong> cos2θ = −½ → ref = 60°<br>
      2θ = 120° + 360°n  OR  2θ = −120° + 360°n<br>
      θ = 60° + 180°n  OR  θ = −60° + 180°n,  n∈ℤ ✓ (4)<br><br>
      <strong>(c)</strong> tanθ = −√3 → ref = 60°<br>
      θ = 180° − 60° + 180°n = 120° + 180°n,  n∈ℤ ✓ (4)
    </div>
